>About Guangzhou<br/></strong></span></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>City layout</strong></span></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:arial, helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">The central districts of Guangzhou stretch along a waterfront that runs south and then east along the Pearl River. The Old City (dating to the<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"md-crosslink\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255) none repeat scroll 0% 0%; color: rgb(16, 101, 150); font-style: normal; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: underline; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:arial, helvetica,sans-seriffont-family:arial, helvetica,sans-seriffont-family:arial, helvetica,sans-serif\">Ming dynasty</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>and now mostly in the Yuexiu district), part of the district of Liwan to the west, and Tianhe district to the east are located on the north bank. On the south bank is the district of Haizhu, formerly largely industrial but now more given over to business offices, financial institutions, and other service-related activities. All these districts now<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"md-dictionary-link md-dictionary-tt-off\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255) none repeat scroll 0% 0%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom: 2px dotted rgb(16, 101, 150); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">comprise</a></span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span>the core area of the city.</span></span></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:arial, helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-trans