nd-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Clifford</span><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">School is one of China&#39;s largest private school and is located in the Clifford Estates gated community. Clifford Estates,&nbsp;</span>in<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>Panyu, covers an area of 500 hectares and has a population of more than 200,000, making it the largest gated community in China! Panyu is a very large suburb of Guangzhou (Canton) in South China.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> <br/></span></span></em></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span><em style=\"font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif, websafe; font-size: 17.5px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"><img src=\"https://uploads.100chinajobs.com/20191128/ae4c68c1ce22b8cac81fcae78a3dad5f.jpg\"/></span></span></em></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#000000\"><span><em style=\"font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif, websafe; font-size: 17.5px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 82, 150); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif, websafe; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">A Bird&#39;s Eye View of Clifford Estates</span></span></span></em></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#000000\"><span><em style=\"font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif, websafe; font-size: 17.5px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif, websafe; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif, websafe; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">Clifford Estates is a large gated community consisting of apartments, villas and houses. The estates cover an area of more than 500 hectares with about 60,000 homes and a population of more than 200,000 representing people from 70 countries and regions.</span></span></span></span></em></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#000000\"><span><em style=\"font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif, websafe; font-size: 17.5px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif, websafe; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif, websafe; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif, websafe; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">In 2014, Clifford Estates commenced a major transformation that will see the building of a large shopping, recreation and entertainment area (called Clifford Wonderland), several apartment buildings, a brand new hospital building, a hotel, roads, a tunnel as well as, access to Guangzhou&#39;s extensive underground transport network. In August 2016, Clifford Wonderland, the large residential and commercial shopping center, was opened to the public. In October 2017, the new modern hospital building opened. The Clifford Resort Center is undergoing renovations and there is still a lot of construction going on but most of it should be completed by 2020.</span><br/></span></span></span></span></em></span></span></p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif, websafe; font-size: 17.5px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">One of the more exciting construction projects for&nbsp;us is the new sports field being built on our campus! It will be comprised of a modern track &amp; field sports facility and an underground parking area with bus pickup and drop off, which we expect to be completed in the spring of 2019! <br/></span></span></p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif, websafe; font-size: 17.5px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">There are eight internal bus routes covering every part of the Estate. The Estate is very green and well landscaped. The teacher’s apartments are well away from the new construction at the south-west end of the Estate. Many of the apartments overlook a large green space called Dafu Mountain, which you can visit and go on a hike.</span></span></p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif, websafe; font-size: 17.5px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;On the Estate, there are many recreational and shopping areas. You can swim, go to the gym, bike, walk, jog or just have fun in the parks and gardens. Clifford teachers have free access to the swimming and fitness complex right across the street from their living apartments. There are also other resort complexes on the Estate with pools and recreational areas.There is also a large hospital on site. It is a private hospital run by the Clifford Group. People come from all over to have access to the excellent medical staff and facilities at the hospital. They have a translation service, a VIP counter for foreigners and the school’s health insurance has direct billing arranged with the hospital.</span></span></p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif, websafe; font-size: 17.5px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;Overall, it is a very pleasant environment to live and work. In fact, there is no real need to ever leave the Estate, but, if you wish to, there are direct buses to and from the Estate to Guangzhou (about 30-40 minutes) and other parts of Southern China, including Hong Kong, Zhuhai, Macau,&nbsp;and the Guangzhou International Airport (about 70-90 minutes away).</span></span></p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif, websafe; font-size: 17.5px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><img src=\"https://uploads.100chinajobs.com/20191128/1dcce86c519cd2f5bd2a3cdf68bdcd4b.jpg\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><br/><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span><em style=\"font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif, websafe; font-size: 17.5px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif, websafe; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif, websafe; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"></span></span></span></span></em></span></span></span><br/></p><p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span><em style=\"font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif, websafe; font-size: 17.5px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"></span></span></em></span></span><br/></p>',NULL,'','',NULL,NULL,'','','','','','','','','','','','',0,0,0,36,NULL,'2019-11-28 06:51:58','2019-11-28 07:27:05'),(99,421,'Eton House International School,Suzhou','',0,0,0,'https://uploads.100chinajobs.com/20191128/56443033e7bb92dd2942d79f37c533d1.jpg','https://uploads.100chinajobs.com/20191128/c4719ee8205939dce2dbd969ba2dee68.mp4','','Chinese name: 苏州伊顿国际学校   EtonHouse International School, Suzhou was set up in 2003 in the Suzhou New District.\r\nThe school is housed in a purpose-built campus in the Suzhou Science and Technology Town, with a land area of approximately 3 hectares. It has a built-in area of 13,800 square metres, including excellent sports facilities such as an indoor heated swimming pool, spacious classrooms, excellent art, science and music facilities, large auditorium, gymnasium, basketball courts, tennis court and a synthetic grass sports field. It offers classes from pre-school to senior years (ages 2 to 18). EtonHouse Suzhou is a fully authorised International Baccalaureate World School for Primary Years (IB PYP) and Middle Years (IB MYP). For our Senior Years Programme, we provide IB Diploma programmes (IB DP) and the Advanced Placement International Diploma (AP) or the EtonHouse High School Diploma.','','','','https://uploads.100chinajobs.com/20191128/432857c644c5dde9a64878ac523bbe72.png','Suzhou, alternately romanized as Soochow, is a major city located in southeastern Jiangsu Province of East China, about 100 km northwest of Shanghai. It is a major economic center and focal point of trade and commerce, and the second largest city in the province, after its capital Nanjing. The city is situated on the lower reaches of the Yangtze River and the shores of Lake Tai and belongs to the Yangtze River Delta region. Administratively, Suzhou is a prefecture-level city with a population of 4.33 million in its city proper, and a total resident population of 10.58 million in its administrative area. Its urban population grew at an unprecedented rate of 6.5% between 2000 and 2014, which is the highest among cities with more than 5 million people.','<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\">About Suzhou</span><br/></strong></p><p><strong>History</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">Suzhou, the cradle of Wu culture, is one of the oldest towns in the Yangtze Basin. By the Spring and Autumn period of the Zhou, local tribes named the Gou Wu are recorded living in the area which would become the modern city of Suzhou. These tribes formed villages on the edges of the hills above the wetlands surrounding Lake Tai. Sima Qian&#39;s Records of the Grand Historian records traditional accounts that the Zhou lord Taibo established the state of Wu at nearby Wuxi during the 11th century BC,</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong><a href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(96, 0, 144); text-decoration: none; touch-action: manipulation; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Canals and historic districts</a></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: 